lombok-data-do-not-use-getter - Lombok Data Fixer

USAGE:
    lombok-data-do-not-use-getter <source-filename>

DESCRIPTION:
    Fix Lombok @Data annotations to use doNotUseGetters option.
    Removes existing @ToString and adds @ToString(doNotUseGetters = true)
    above @Data annotation.

ARGUMENTS:
    source-filename
        Java source file to fix (required)

EXAMPLES:
    lombok-data-do-not-use-getter MyClass.java
    lombok-data-do-not-use-getter src/model/User.java
